      <body>
         <div type="letter" xml:id="d3e154">
            <pb n="1" facs="0012_000192_000205_0001.jpg" xml:id="d3e155"/>
            <p>Blains&apos; Cross Roads</p>
            <p>Dec. 21./63</p>
            <pb n="2" facs="0012_000192_000205_0002.jpg" xml:id="d3e165"/>
            <p>Hd. Qrs. 1st Div. Cav. Corps</p>
            <p>Blains Cross Roads</p>
            <p>Decr. 21st 1863</p>
            <p>Dear Father</p>
            <p>I am well but have not time to write &amp; have not had time for several days. Will as soon as possible. A man going through in the morning will take this. The Bag has come &amp; I was much pleased with its contents.</p>
            <p>Much love to all of you</p>
            <p>Your aff son</p>
            <p>Watson B Smith</p>
            <p>St. &amp; A.A.A.G.</p>
            <p>1st Div. Cav. Corps</p>
         </div>
      </body>
